FBIS4-16084 "drsov072_s_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-072 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 Georgia Commission Formed To Reorganize Financial System Commission Formed To Reorganize Financial System LD1304173794 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY in Russian 1446 GMT 13 Apr 94 LD1304173794 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY Russian BFN [Text] With the aim of drawing up measures to overcome the deep financial crisis in the country, achieving financial stability, and improving the current situation, the Cabinet of Ministers of the Republic of Georgia has decreed the creation of a government commission charged with reorganizing the financial system in the Republic of Georgia. The commission will be chaired by Deputy Prime Minister Temur Basilia and will include the heads of relevant agencies, the National Bank, and the Science Institute.
